<p>As a human being you are capable of <strong>thoughts</strong>, <strong>words</strong> and <strong>actions</strong>.</p>

<p>We also feel <strong>emotions</strong>.</p>

<p>If we harm someone with our thoughts, words and actions then their emotional reactions will be stored and returned to us later.</p>

